data.description: Rare opportunity for investors and savvy homeowners to add instant equity to this classic 3-bed, 1-bath raised ranch in Tinley Park!  This home offers a large living room, formal dining room, an eat-in kitchen, spacious bedrooms, a full lower level that could be finished for additional living space, and an attached garage.  Prime location.  Sold as-is.  No survey will be provided.
